{"tid":823589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"順著年份看土地歷史(好小字)","createTime":"2018-09-16T23:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T00:12:10.000Z","uid":90323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c535c6fce3f215bbe19f5a5a79b8032f739a41ed","tid":823589,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"在1898年的之前, 清朝的時侯， 即君權神授嘅時代， 其實原住民就已經有屬於自已嘅土地。<br />\n<br />\n01博評-香港地<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%B0/129500/%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E5%8E%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E6%93%81%E6%9C%89-%E4%B8%81%E6%AC%8A-%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E8%A2%AB%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E8%AA%AA%E8%B5%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%258D%259A%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%25B0%2F129500%2F%25E5%258D%259A%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2593%2581%25E6%259C%2589-%25E4%25B8%2581%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E7%2595%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E8%25B5%25B7&d=h5bjqPS1ZrM2LFwuuWGyz%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=e9a5dffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%B0/129500/%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E5%8E%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E6%93%81%E6%9C%89-%E4%B8%81%E6%AC%8A-%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E8%A2%AB%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E8%AA%AA%E8%B5%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n在1900 年，政府建立新界填土法例， 第17條說明了政府是每塊土地的擁有者， 村民不能決定自已土地的用途。<br />\n01倡議 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/113366/01%E5%80%A1%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%9545%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%2F113366%2F01%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%259545%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%258D%25B5%25E6%25A6%2582%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AE%2580&d=h5bjqPS1ZrM2LFwuuWGyz%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=fdeae0be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/113366/01%E5%80%A1%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%9545%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80</a> <br />\n<br />\n在1972年， 民政事務處宣佈小型房屋政策時強調， 小型房屋政策是短期策略， 目標是為了解決村間低質素居住環境的問題， 因為當年村間的居住情況很差。但當年漏了條款， 變成今天的丁屋任起，然而 政府有權改變自已做錯的事。<br />\n明報專訊<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20140209183134/http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/News/20120109/HK-gna1_er.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20140209183134%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaovan.com%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20120109%2FHK-gna1_er.htm&d=h5bjqPS1ZrM2LFwuuWGyz%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b749faa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20140209183134/http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/News/20120109/HK-gna1_er.htm</a> <br />\n<br />\n補充資料<br />\n01倡議 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/113366/01%E5%80%A1%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%9545%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%2F113366%2F01%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%259545%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E9%2597%259